AOMEI Backupper is an all-in-one, simple and safe Windows backup and clone software. It integrates series of practical utilities to protect your data and system. Key features: System, hard disk, partition, files and folders backup and restore. File Sync.; Supports full, incremental, differential, event-triggered scheduling and automatic backups; Backup/Sync file to cloud drive desktop app; Universal restore, selective restore, restore from bootable media; Disk and system clone for upgrading HDD or transferring OS; Mount, compress, split, encrypt, and check backup images; Email notifications, view logs, and export/import backup tasks; More features… System Requirements: 
Windows 10/ 8.1/ 8/ 7/ Vista/ XP (x32/x64); CPU: Intel Pentium or compatible, 500MHz or faster processor; RAM: 256MB or greater; CD-RW/DVD-RW drive for bootable media creation Publisher:
